casebody.data:
Travonta BERRY, Appellant(s)/Petitioner(s),
v.
Daniel JUNIOR, etc., Appellee(s)/Respondent(s), CASE NO.: 3D17-2508 District Court of Appeal of Florida, Third District. DECEMBER 01, 2017 SUAREZ, SALTER and SCALES, JJ., concur.

Following review of the petition for writ of habeas corpus, and the response and reply thereto, it is ordered that said petition is hereby denied.
